{"tid":2160992,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"支持堅守議會圍爐區","createTime":"2020-08-17T10:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T13:59:18.000Z","uid":271176,"like":27,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"fc7b536be4fb2f27cdd71c13dd7ee1f61fd57159","tid":2160992,"uid":271176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"我見出面多數post都係支持拒絕被委任入臨立會，一話要留，就係貪錢，食人血饅頭，唔識玩，所以開個post 俾支持堅守議會的人講原因，希望反對者起碼知道留守者理據<br />\n<br />\n我先講，首先我認同臨立會冇市民授權，亦都認同咁嘅情況都唔退，會俾人睇死你唔敢退。<br />\n另外，我認同政府要推惡法，立會冇方法阻止<br />\n<br />\n但我仍然覺得要守，因為唔守的話，政府可以極速以少代價立惡法，令到想逃離香港嘅人走唔到，想留守香港嘅人發唔到聲，我隨便列10條法案<br />\n<br />\n1.假新聞法<br />\n2.侮辱公職人員罪<br />\n3記者登記<br />\n4移民不可拿強積金，要等65歲<br />\n5立會議員疑犯刑事案，經半數議員同意可停職<br />\n6眾籌法（禁612,國際線）<br />\n7.國民教育法，加強教科書審查<br />\n8禁公投法（視為集會，受公安條例約束）<br />\n9加辣公安條例，進一步降低暴動，非法集結門檻，加強罰則<br />\n10取消BNO移民者居港資格<br />\n11強制檢驗，健康碼<br />\n<br />\n俾多30分鐘我，我可以多寫50條，當然有市民派在立會，的確阻止不到惡法，但能夠延緩惡法， 組織輿論，讓對方付出代價。例如如果本地能輕鬆在立會過23條，根本唔駛用國安法，國際反應亦唔會咁強。好多對對方得益微的惡法，亦不值得去推（立會冇阻力另計）。如果今後一年，立會全為共派，香港人真係at their mercy（有嗎？）<br />\n<br />\n最後，我唔覺得入咗臨立會，世界就會當冇事，除非佢地過去一年瞓著咗<br />\n<br />\n最後嘅最後 ，留任/拒絕委任各有理據，各有缺憾。根本出題者就係你點答都死，要討論，唔要批鬥"},{"pid":"d95cdd14b3eff37bfa09afe4e3174abd6a40faa0","tid":2160992,"uid":61914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:12:04.000Z","msg":"明報有個summary table已經講咗就算全體留任都改變唔到絕大部份法案無法抵擋既事實"},{"pid":"fced2332bcf63706c7f6c5d4f911d044fafd5599","tid":2160992,"uid":147182,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:12:58.000Z","msg":"樓主支持啲寫希望泛民繼續每個月有十皮(但要錢做野個寫就眾籌)會比較直接同convincing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81e64350afb95b168a877524d51b3261724bab0","tid":2160992,"uid":147182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:14:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主寫希望泛民繼續每個月有十皮袋(但要錢做野個時就眾籌)會比較直接同convincing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"689deb988fcbd0712cf6c68ece04afc28c73eebb","tid":2160992,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:14:35.000Z","msg":"總辭與留任以外第三條路： 初選勝者指示泛民投票，泛民薪津悉數交出<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2160646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2160646</a>"},{"pid":"aec68f488617a3e83a3dbb25a93d2019c1e612be","tid":2160992,"uid":125720,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:15:49.000Z","msg":"泛民一係唔出席一係就棄權架啦<br />\n阻閪到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9b053bab7d170f478fe1137d231ec4708ec8c6","tid":2160992,"uid":271176,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"d95cdd14b3eff37bfa09afe4e3174abd6a40faa0","tid":2160992,"uid":61914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:12:04.000Z","msg":"明報有個summary table已經講咗就算全體留任都改變唔到絕大部份法案無法抵擋既事實"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:16:34.000Z","msg":"國歌法攪咗幾個月，係擋唔到，但係用咗時間，如果出惡法，冇反對，幾個月可以過好多條<br />\n<br />\n市民派的確冇能力反對，只能阻礙，增加成本"},{"pid":"86bc6e2aa2c0e9092d319ca401195cc5915cc0a4","tid":2160992,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:16:41.000Z","msg":"泛民成主留<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26401ca81362afa18ad5f9f6a2206ac156a0518a","tid":2160992,"uid":147182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"689deb988fcbd0712cf6c68ece04afc28c73eebb","tid":2160992,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:14:35.000Z","msg":"總辭與留任以外第三條路： 初選勝者指示泛民投票，泛民薪津悉數交出<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2160646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2160646</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:17:01.000Z","msg":"悉數交出你老母咩 留低唔係為份糧為咩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5bafcb8644e6bbf0ba311b163f5e0858dc1a00","tid":2160992,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:17:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e8461a47d4502502265be84cbadeb29c0bd95d2","tid":2160992,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:17:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a78a1a40ff73947a2ffe23a648380c91544de63c","tid":2160992,"uid":271176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:18:47.000Z","msg":"討論係講理據，批鬥係分陣營，大家識分"},{"pid":"b15e28dbed3e64780374ff6a38568c331001b2fa","tid":2160992,"uid":31151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a78a1a40ff73947a2ffe23a648380c91544de63c","tid":2160992,"uid":271176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:18:47.000Z","msg":"討論係講理據，批鬥係分陣營，大家識分"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"依家個問題反對留既 已經比晒理據同證據 但支持果班仍然係扮睇唔到"},{"pid":"d376c082b66fbfb6e55c43f003fcdf9e1032f6d5","tid":2160992,"uid":109570,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:21:15.000Z","msg":"本身都覺得要總辭,原因都係個D: <br />\n<br />\n佢要過都係會過<br />\n臨立會冇認受性,入去姐係比認受性佢<br />\nETC 不盡例<br />\n<br />\n但係諗落都係覺得要守. <br />\n<br />\n一黎你講左因為唔守的話，政府可以極速以少代價立惡法 <br />\n<br />\n二黎我地KEEP住做都唔一定比到個認受性政府(臨立會), 依加全世界都知香港咩事, 個橙爛到冇得再爛, 入去只係想確保政府唔可以極速以少代價立惡法<br />\n<br />\n三黎 我覺得無論點都好, 中共都會分化你. 我覺得最好係做個有公信力既民調 再決定點行<br />\n<br />\nsorry 少少1999 一陣返到屋企再同你地討論下<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">乜都好, 一定要齊心 咪比中共分化</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c36b8a654a0ecb811af16cc4eef3cd19204428d2","tid":2160992,"uid":47144,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:21:29.000Z","msg":"咁您又要認同阻唔到，<br />\n您列多100條例子出嚟都係阻唔到<br />\n<br />\n你話離任嘅話政府可以低成本過法案<br />\n泛民留任點樣去增加成本？<br />\n<br />\n同埋你又認同泛民留任無民意授權<br />\n<br />\n你其實係唔係曲？"},{"pid":"e784254b3268c070a917c3bdc4c3885f0b7986a0","tid":2160992,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xt7MEXa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXt7MEXa.jpg&h=eb9473ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9894237cde9209156d76e1cf98afea06b695c951","tid":2160992,"uid":331421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:23:47.000Z","msg":"唔多啲惡法點加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9732e4d643763574aba76ad1a419b254945b6f","tid":2160992,"uid":35233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:27:01.000Z","msg":"雖然留任無乜大作為，但總辭有咩咁好？"},{"pid":"649ae99349dbf5bd44d1687815f122e264532891","tid":2160992,"uid":55197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:28:01.000Z","msg":"哦！另外方面諗，支共港共就係要你班飯民係到做永遠嘅反對派，咁支共控制嘅（真）議會都有反對聲音，個（真）議會就冇咁難睇，反對聲音大我就減慢議案通過速度，又可以比反對派有下台階<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1838e911ab6ae470bfae50b8d66c3da7832ae046","tid":2160992,"uid":46161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:28:59.000Z","msg":"你留底都一樣阻唔到..... 仲做爛自己個名<br />\n幾個月人工都咁著緊！"},{"pid":"ac1a01919050898c96295f953a229211a76bdc0e","tid":2160992,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:30:11.000Z","msg":"佢而家立惡法要經立法會？"},{"pid":"4f335c456c2c2e8cf9acb1485eba03ff17388215","tid":2160992,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:30:13.000Z","msg":"你留低人工捐一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db0fa353a4df6df0a37974094233267a26eddfa","tid":2160992,"uid":301666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:38:20.000Z","msg":"杯葛臨立會 &gt; 推行更箝制示威自由嘅惡法 &gt; 下年DQ參選人 &gt; 街頭同議會戰線都無 &gt; 等美國接濟？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人話民主派留喺度都會照過惡法，但事實係<br />\n<br />\n(a) 留喺度最少可以拖延時間<br />\n<br />\n(b) 拖延時間期間又可以炒熱事件、聚集民氣，同街頭抗爭相輔相成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又有人話，外國見到香港議會正常運作，就唔會做嘢<br />\n<br />\n(a) 你當外國係傻，完全唔知立法會偽民主，亦都唔知道我哋加入只係為咗寸土必爭？<br />\n<br />\n(b) 照呢個諗法，全部走晒即係同外國講「我哋自動放棄抗爭機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」，總辭之後外國會覺得香港唔抵幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbbe23ded39863d40bc9a51a63260607d5ef58a","tid":2160992,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:39:44.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">守住份糧就夠，香港前途食屎啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港獨立咗仲點做反對派呀"},{"pid":"d6b940d665a811fb562635357cf4b09a1d1dab45","tid":2160992,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f335c456c2c2e8cf9acb1485eba03ff17388215","tid":2160992,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:30:13.000Z","msg":"你留低人工捐一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:40:02.000Z","msg":"係一個幾好嘅做法，而家好多支持總辭嘅人就係覺得「飯民」要keep住啲人工<br />\n<br />\n宣布捐人工，可以令大家排除呢個猜測"},{"pid":"b750f01c569375eb07fbaf64a5373805f9b6cc7d","tid":2160992,"uid":271176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c36b8a654a0ecb811af16cc4eef3cd19204428d2","tid":2160992,"uid":47144,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:21:29.000Z","msg":"咁您又要認同阻唔到，<br />\n您列多100條例子出嚟都係阻唔到<br />\n<br />\n你話離任嘅話政府可以低成本過法案<br />\n泛民留任點樣去增加成本？<br />\n<br />\n同埋你又認同泛民留任無民意授權<br />\n<br />\n你其實係唔係曲？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"我意思係港共要推，留唔留都阻唔到，留係到會增加成本；推一條惡法開2次會就過，同開20次會先過，邊邊會出更多惡法"},{"pid":"70f148eb0e734b379fb25a340a3bd410db7fcac0","tid":2160992,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:43:47.000Z","msg":"幫推啦  呢幾日已經係不同post reply左好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係咁 又一次有堆五毛pr帶風分化+大量真心膠<br />\n<br />\n反對唔緊要 都要俾d理由 <br />\n講講下又變左反泛民 咁反泛民關臨立咩事 你初選都要出黎反啦咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋純為反泛民而去&quot;辭職&ldquo;<br />\n咁唔係臨立既問題"},{"pid":"1fc63b383b5b1cda54996e5c8ef2fb637d5767b7","tid":2160992,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc